{
  "stem": "16503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he like got us together and he said, what do you think of this idea, like us living the four of us together?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, well, to be quite honest, I prefer where I am living.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And with that, I'm terribly sorry because that was my last chance to live for the last time as a unit, a family, under one roof.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father, as I said, was a extremely forward-looking person or had it in him the humanity, which today it's called humanity understanding, and he said, look, if you are happy where you are, I think we should leave it that way.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, when I first got into the children's home-- and that was three weeks after we got into Theresienstadt, I was terribly unhappy because I was independent, but I was mama's girl.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here I was, and she had to leave me in the evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I would be screaming and, and crying, saying, oh mom, please, please, please don't leave me here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this, I'm sorry for that because I must have caused her an awful lot of heartache because now, being grow-up, having three children of my own, how often did my-- did I get a sitter and the children would cry and I would go to the first telephone box and call back.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the sitter would say, oh they're fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are playing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She came-- she had to go to her accommodation that night, seeing me crying, and saying, oh my dear God, that poor child is there alone.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, I was alone, but I had 30-- 29-- other girls plus the supervisor, and within a week, this has eased completely.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I'm sorry that I caused her that problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
